            <body>
                
                                        <p>Ego <persName key="d1e12947" xml:id="d1e135737">Willelmus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324406" xml:id="d1e135739" corresp="Beaune (Côte-d'Or)">Berna</placeName>, dominus
                            de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324973" xml:id="d1e135742" corresp="Paceio">Paceio</placeName>
                        </persName>, per manum <persName key="d1e12954" xml:id="d1e135745">comitisse
                            Matildis</persName> quondam uxo<lb n="2" break="no" />ris <persName key="d1e12960" xml:id="d1e135750">Vidonis, comitis <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#99026" xml:id="d1e135752" corresp="Nevers (Nièvre, Nevers)">Nivernensis</placeName>
                        </persName>, dedi et concessi fratribus ęcclesie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e135755" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> terram quam
                        juxta <lb n="3" /> domum suam de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#101036" xml:id="d1e135761" corresp="Sancerre (Cher, Bourges, Sancerre)">Sansueriis</placeName> absque assensu meo
                        exartaverant et tenebant et quicquid habe<lb n="4" break="no" />bant apud
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#101036" xml:id="d1e135766" corresp="Sancerre (Cher, Bourges, Sancerre)">Sansuerias</placeName> et in finagio de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324466" xml:id="d1e135769" corresp="Laignes (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Lania</placeName> ex dono <persName key="d1e12966" xml:id="d1e135772">Willelmi comitis <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#99026" xml:id="d1e135774" corresp="Nevers (Nièvre, Nevers)">Nivernensis</placeName>
                        </persName> qui po<lb n="5" break="no" />stea fuit conversus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#281491" xml:id="d1e135780" corresp="ordre des chartreux">Cartusiensis</orgName> qui sicut
                        in scriptis <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e135783" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fontene(tensium)</orgName> continetur laudante <lb n="6" />
                        <persName key="d1e12972" xml:id="d1e135787">Willelmo filio suo</persName>
                        donavit in elemosinam abbatie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e135790" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> apud <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#101036" xml:id="d1e135794" corresp="Sancerre (Cher, Bourges, Sancerre)">Sansuerias</placeName> locum
                            habi<lb n="7" break="no" />tationis cujusdam hominis Dei nomine <persName key="d1e12978" xml:id="d1e135799">Galterii</persName> qui ibidem
                        religiose habitabat et pra<lb n="8" break="no" />ta que idem <persName key="d1e12984" xml:id="d1e135804">Galterius</persName> tenebat et
                        insuper de proximo <term>mareschio</term> ad excolendum in prata ad opus <lb n="9" /> grangie <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324452" xml:id="d1e135813" corresp="Fontaines-en-Duesmois (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Fontanarum</placeName> quantum necesse esset et omnes aasencias suas in
                        terris de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324466" xml:id="d1e135816" corresp="Laignes (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Lania</placeName> et pastu<lb n="10" break="no" />ras omnibus animalibus
                        suis in bosco et in plano. Hoc donum prefatus <persName key="d1e12991" xml:id="d1e135821">comes Willelmus</persName>
                        <lb n="11" /> fecit in camera sua apud <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#101449" xml:id="d1e135826" corresp="Tonnerre (Yonne, Avallon, Tonnerrois)">Tornodorum</placeName> anno ab incarnatione Domini
                        millesimo .<num>c<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>. xxx<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>. iiii<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>.</num>
                        <lb n="12" /> Hoc postea laudavit prefatus <persName key="d1e12997" xml:id="d1e135842">Vido comes <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#99026" xml:id="d1e135844" corresp="Nevers (Nièvre, Nevers)">Nivernensis</placeName>
                        </persName> et inde cartam sigillo suo <lb n="13" /> munitam predictis
                        fratribus fecit. Et ego similiter ejus exemplum secutus, predictis fratribus
                            <lb n="14" />
                        <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e135850" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> prece
                            <persName key="d1e13003" xml:id="d1e135854">comitisse
                            Matildis</persName> et per manum ejus laudavi et confirmavi omnia que<lb n="15" break="no" />cumque in finagio de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324466" xml:id="d1e135859" corresp="Laignes (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Lania</placeName> usque ad hanc diem acquisierant et
                        ante habuerant et te<lb n="16" break="no" />nuerant et omnes res omnes res
                        eorum in toto posse meo in tuitione et defensione mea recepi et de <lb n="17" /> his adversus omnes homines garentiam me portaturum promisi. Pro
                        his etiam ha<lb n="18" break="no" />bui de beneficio ęcclesie decem libras et
                        pro duobus bubus .lx<hi rend="superscript">a</hi>. solidos. Ut autem hoc <lb n="19" /> ratum et inconvulsum habeatur inconvulsum habeatur inposterum
                        cartam hanc fieri precepi et appensio<lb n="20" break="no" />ne sigilli
                            <persName key="d1e13009" xml:id="d1e135876">Galterii fratris mei comitis
                            de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325054" xml:id="d1e135878" corresp="Brena">Brena</placeName>
                        </persName> munire feci. Unde sunt testes <lb n="21" />
                        <persName key="d1e13015" xml:id="d1e135882">Matildis quondam comitissa
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#99026" xml:id="d1e135884" corresp="Nevers (Nièvre, Nevers)">Nivernensis</placeName>
                        </persName>, per cujus manum factum est, <persName key="d1e13021" xml:id="d1e135888">Willelmus prior <lb n="22" />
                            <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e135891" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e13028" xml:id="d1e135894">Philippus de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325251" xml:id="d1e135896" corresp="Corabœuf (Côte-d'Or, Arnay-le-Duc)">Corte
                                Raboti</placeName>
                        </persName> et <persName key="d1e13034" xml:id="d1e135899">Hugo de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324349" xml:id="d1e135901" corresp="Quincy-le-Vicomte (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Quinceio</placeName>
                        </persName>, monachi, <persName key="d1e13040" xml:id="d1e135904">Petrus
                                prepo<lb n="23" break="no" />situs de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324973" xml:id="d1e135908" corresp="Paceio">Paceio</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e13046" xml:id="d1e135911">Hugo major de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324466" xml:id="d1e135913" corresp="Laignes (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Lania</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e13052" xml:id="d1e135916">Columbus filius
                                <persName key="d1e13058" xml:id="d1e135918">Marini</persName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e13065" xml:id="d1e135922">Petrus
                                    <addName>Ali<lb n="24" break="no" />reius</addName>
                        </persName> et <persName key="d1e13071" xml:id="d1e135929">Garinus</persName> nepos ejus et <persName key="d1e13077" xml:id="d1e135932">Willelmus <addName>
                                <foreign>Chainart</foreign>
                            </addName>
                        </persName>. Actum anno ab in<lb n="25" break="no" />carnatione Domini
                        millessimo centesimo nonagesimo secundo.</p>
                
            </body>
